      • fileRecoverPreviousVersion

        void fileRecoverPreviousVersion​(Serializable fileId,
                                boolean acceptNotPreviousVersion)
                         throws DmsException
        Delete last version of this file and mark previous as current active. If no previous version available, operation must be aborted and error must be raised.
        Parameters:
        fileVersionId - the file version id
        acceptNotPreviousVersion - if false and not previous version located (for instance the only one) exception will be raise, else file will continue without any version
        Throws:
        DmsException
